---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import rooms from "../data/rooms.json";

const BOOKING_BASE = "https://be.guestsage.com/pl/0bf0dc4c-089f-42f4-8bf0-3ea22a76ad8a";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pokoje i apartamenty — Hotel Zacisze ★★★ Turawa"
  description="Komfortowe pokoje Classic, Lux i apartamenty w ogrodzie. 150 m od plaży Jeziora Turawskiego, otoczone sosnowym lasem."
  canonicalPath="/pokoje"
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <img src="/assets/current/hotel/Copy of 101.jpg" alt="Domki hotelowe wśród sosen" class="page-header-img" />
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <h1>Pokoje i apartamenty</h1>
      <p>Komfort ★★★ w sercu sosnowego lasu — 150 m od plaży</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="rooms-main">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="rooms-grid">
        {rooms.map((room) => (
          <article class="room-card">
            <a href={room.slug} class="room-img-link">
              <img src={room.image} alt={room.title} loading="lazy" class="room-img" />
            </a>
            <div class="room-body">
              <div class="room-capacity">{room.capacity}</div>
              <h2 class="room-title">
                <a href={room.slug}>{room.title}</a>
              </h2>
              <p class="room-desc">{room.description}</p>
              <div class="room-actions">
                <a href={room.slug} class="room-details">Szczegóły</a>
                <a href={BOOKING_BASE} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="room-book">Rezerwuj</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>

      <aside class="rooms-note">
        <p>Wszystkie pokoje i apartamenty objęte są <strong>gwarancją najniższej ceny</strong> przy bezpośredniej rezerwacji. Śniadanie i dostęp do strefy SPA wliczone w każdy nocleg.</p>
        <a href={BOOKING_BASE} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Sprawdź dostępność i rezerwuj</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    position: relative;
    height: 50vh;
    min-height: 320px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    background: var(--dark);
  }

  .page-header-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .page-header-inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1200px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--surface);
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .rooms-main {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .rooms-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .room-card {
    display: grid;
    border: 1px solid var(--muted);
    background: var(--surface);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .room-img-link { display: block; overflow: hidden; }

  .room-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    display: block;
  }

  .room-card:hover .room-img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .room-body {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .room-capacity {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .room-title {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .room-title a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .room-title a:hover { color: var(--text-secondary); }

  .room-desc {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .room-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .room-details {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .room-details:hover { color: var(--text-secondary); }

  .room-book {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 0.45rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--surface);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--dark);
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .room-book:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .rooms-note {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--muted);
    padding-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .rooms-note p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--surface);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid var(--dark);
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .rooms-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .rooms-note { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; }
    .rooms-note p { margin: 0; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 960px) {
    .rooms-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
